Create and run a new flask app

mkdir new_project
cd  new_project
python3 -m venv venv && source venv/bin/activate
pip install Flask
export FLASK_APP=app.py
flask run



export FLASK_DEBUG=1 ==> each change made in code will be synchronized and seen directly into website



this command adds all the requirements of the app automatically in the requirements file
pip freeze > requirements.txt

Build docker image
docker build -t my-app .













































